============================================================
SUMMARY STATISTICS: % of Roofline Achieved
============================================================
  Mean roofline achieved:  72.1%
  Min roofline achieved:   56.8%
  Max roofline achieved:   82.6%

Interpretation:
  Roofline % = roofline_time / real_time * 100
  100% = real matches roofline (perfect HW utilization)
   75% = real is 1.33x slower than roofline
   50% = real is 2x slower than roofline
  >100% = roofline overestimates latency (too conservative)
